        "subject": "LU-4984 llite: check for integer overflow in hsm user request",
        "message": "LU-4984 llite: check for integer overflow in hsm user request\n\nCheck to make sure total size of request does not overflow when\ncalculated.  Return -1 from hur_len() if it does overflow.\n\nThis is a backport to b2_5 from\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/10615/6\nLustre-commit: 744b4f9253e1740eb7454a9a33fa6d4b06920dcb\n\nSigned-off-by: Nathaniel Clark <nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6a3ca50c53ff38dab4165f20dac6fa00eb888df2\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\n"
